text: George Milligan may refer to: * George Milligan (moderator) (1860–1934), Scottish minister of the Church of Scotland * George Milligan (politician) (born 1934), American politician in the state of Iowa * George Milligan (footballer) (1891–?), Scottish footballer * George Milligan (Biblical scholar) (1860–1934), professor at Warwick University
